## Error Handling

- Each phase retries up to 3 times on fixable errors (build failures, syntax errors).
- If a phase fails after 3 attempts, STOP and report the error clearly. Do not proceed to the next phase.
- Proto generation errors (Phase 3) block all subsequent phases.
- Build validation errors (Phase 9) should be traced back to the originating phase and fixed there.

## Progress Tracking

Provide progress updates after each phase:

```
[0/10]  Research and discovery complete -- awaiting confirmation
[1/10]  Proto definitions created
